{// Simple track to suppress outputs.
    val limit = z.textbox("최대 카테고리 수", "10").toString
    val column = z.angular("column").toString
    val group = z.select("그룹", categoricalColumns(0), categoricalColumns.map(x => (x, x)))
    
    z.angularBind("limit", limit) // Override the dynamic form "numBins".
    z.angularBind("group", group)
    
    z.run("20180519-011149_794588296")  // !!! Copy and paste your paragraph ID!
}

%sql
WITH
target (
SELECT
    ${column} AS x,
    ${group} AS grp
FROM ${table}
),
grp_cnt (
SELECT x, grp, COUNT(*) AS grp_cnt
FROM target
GROUP BY x, grp
),
x_cnt (
SELECT x, SUM(grp_cnt) AS x_cnt
FROM grp_cnt
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x_cnt DESC
LIMIT ${limit}
)
SELECT *
FROM grp_cnt JOIN x_cnt USING (x)
ORDER BY x_cnt DESC
